@startuml
title Context Sources And Budget

skinparam backgroundColor #F7F1E6
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam dpi 135
skinparam defaultFontName Georgia
skinparam defaultFontSize 15
skinparam TitleFontSize 20
skinparam NoteFontSize 14
skinparam ArrowFontSize 13
skinparam ArrowColor #5E5A53
skinparam PackageBorderColor #1D1D1D
skinparam PackageFontColor #161616
skinparam RectangleBorderColor #1D1D1D
skinparam RectangleBackgroundColor #F2E9D9
skinparam RectangleFontColor #161616
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #F5EBDD
skinparam NoteBorderColor #8C2721
skinparam NoteFontColor #7B1E1E
skinparam TitleFontColor #161616
skinparam RectangleRoundCorner 10

left to right direction

package "Context sources" #E8DDD0 {
  rectangle "CLAUDE.md /\nRules" as rules
  rectangle "Persistent Memory" as persistent
  rectangle "Session Memory" as session
  rectangle "Conversation Messages" as messages

  rules --> messages
  persistent --> messages
  session --> messages
}

package "Budget axis" #F3E6CD {
  rectangle "Effective Context Window" as w1
  rectangle "Warning Buffer" as w2
  rectangle "Error Buffer" as w3
  rectangle "Autocompact Threshold" as w4
  rectangle "Manual Compact Buffer" as w5

  w1 --> w2
  w2 --> w3
  w3 --> w4
  w4 --> w5
}

messages -[#8C2721]-> w1 : consumed against

note bottom of messages
治理重点不在“消息条数”，
而在不同来源的规则、
记忆和对话如何一起
占用上下文预算。
end note

@enduml
